- Move actions to core classes or the new Smb4KActions class.
- Add ability to download files with smbget.
- Implement profiles.
- Allow several filemanagers.
- Mount shares by drag and drop into the shares view.
- Implement more 'net' commands:
  + 'rap printq' for info about and deletion of print jobs. 
- Use already existing authentication information for hosts
  and shares (e.g. provided by Dolphin).
- Save authentication information in such way, that other
  programs can use it as well.
- Introduce Plasma applet that can browse the network
  neighborhood and shows the mounted shares.
